ts-awards/billboard-single|title=#1 Girl Billboard Singles|website=[[Allmusic]]|accessdate=2011-10-22}}\n*For '''\"Mrs. Right\"''': {{cite magazine |url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=mindless behavior|chart=Hot 100}}|title=Billboard Hot 100 71\u201380|magazine=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2011-10-27}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\" | [[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs|US R&B]]<br><ref>Peak positions for R&B/Hip-Hop songs:\n*For '''\"My Girl\"''': {{cite magazine |url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2011-06-11/r-b-hip-hop-songs?order=drop|title=R&B/Hip-Hop Sings \u2013 Biggest Fall for June 11, 2011|magazine=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2011-10-22}}\n*For '''\"Mrs. Right\"''': {{cite magazine |url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2011-11-05/r-b-hip-hop-songs|title=R&B/Hip-Hop Sings \u2013 Top 10|magazine=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2011-10-22}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"My Girl\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\"></span>\n|| 2010\n| \u2013 || 40 \n| rowspan=\"4\" | ''#1 Girl''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"[[Mrs. Right]]\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Diggy Simmons]])</span>\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2011\n| 72 || 8 \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Girls Talkin' Bout\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\"></span>\n| \u2013 || 50\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Hello\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\"></span>\n| \u2013 || \u2013 \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Christmas with My Girl\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\"></span>\n| \u2013 || 96 \n| rowspan=\"2\" {{N/A|Non-album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Valentine's Girl\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\"></span>\n|| 2012\n| \u2013 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Keep Her on the Low\"\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2013\n| \u2013 || 47\n| rowspan=\"3\" | ''All Around the World''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"All Around the World\" <br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\"></span>\n| \u2013 || \u2013 \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Used to Be\" <br /><span style=\"fo